• Transparent glass that has been reinforced for scratch resistance

• Hardness : 8~9H

Name: iPhone 5C - Life Proof Fre
Description:
LifeProof frē for iPhone 5C is the strongest, lightest, thinnest and all-protective case. LifeProof frē provides the shockproof, snow-proof, dirt-proof and waterproof protection as you expect from LifeProof.

LifeProof frē completely safeguards your iPhone 5C’s touchscreen with an Built-in scratch protector. Ultra clear and flat, the scratch protector is invisible to your eyes virtually. 

All buttons, speakers, microphones and camera work seamlessly. Also, the clear back window shows off the Apple logo clearly and the sleek silhouette hardly adds to iPhone 5C precision lines.

Key Features
• The thinnest, lightest, all-protective for iPhone 5C case ever made
• Integrated scratch protector provides perfect touchscreen protection
• Protected by The 4 Proofs:
  - Shockproof: Survives drops from 6.6 feet (2m)
  - Snow proof: Completely closed to snow and ice
  - Dirt proof: Totally sealed from dirt and dust
  - Waterproof: Fully submersible to 6.6 feet (2m)
• Full screen protection and functionality
• Complete access to all controls, ports and buttons
• Maximum sound output and clarity
• Anti-reflective optical-glass camera lens
• 1 year warranty

Name: iPhone 5C - Soft Case 2
Description:
The glossy gel moulded case from OSCAR is designed for owners who prefer stylish protection that serves to accentuate the unique look of the iPHONE 5C while protecting it from damage. Moulded from a gel composite, the case is finished with a gloss layer infused with gloss particles.

All of the iPHONE 5C buttons are easily accessible while in the Oscar glossy gel case and photos taken with flash are unaffected. OSCAR offers the most fitting protection for your iPHONE 5C while being completely unobtrusive.

• Strong, durable composite gel that protects against scratches, impacts, dust particles and temperature changes
• Perfectly slim fit with the iPHONE 5C
• Designed and tested to be "flash-friendly"; no interference to iPHONE 5C's built-in flash which causes unwanted flare in photos
• All iPHONE 5C buttons are easily accessible while resting in the case

Name: iPhone 5 / 5S - Revolution
Description:
This innovative case fuses tough protection with a smooth flexible grip. 

The back portion is constructed from top quality robust plastic that gives superior protection to the vulnerable back panel of your phone. 

Surrounding this durable plastic is a softer, flexible rubber-style lip border that conforms to the phone's contours and allows quick and easy encapsulation of your phone in the case's protective shell. 

The contoured non-slip rubber border provides you with a comfortable and secure grip of the phone.

As well as being practical and smart, the dual design creates a visual contrast that accentuates your phone's design.

This well-rounded case is completed with full access to all controls, sockets and the camera, for full functionality.

 

• Robust dual-design 
• Tough, durable back panel that protects against knocks, scratches and dust 
• Soft, non-slip flexible lip border for safe and easy encapsulation of your phone 
• Smooth, firm, comfortable grip 
• Stylish visual contrast between the plastic back panel and coloured lip border

Description:
The HD Universal Easy One Touch 2 provides a safe, versatile and highly functional smartphone mounting solution. Like its predecessors, the One Touch Universal & the One Touch XL, our new One Touch 2 is packed with standard features like the patented one touch locking feature as well as the OSCAR super sticky gel pad. In addition we have designed a new two-step locking lever which ensures your mount can be used on different surfaces. The first locking position can be used for flat, smooth surfaces while the second locking position can be used on curvy textured surfaces that may require more grip. The One Touch 2 also offers a telescopic arm which extends up to 2 additional inches to provide you with even more viewing options when using your mount. The One Touch 2 also provides a new sliding bottom foot. Our redesigned bottom foot ensures that there is no interference with your devices bottom ports. The stickiness of the suction cup is infinite, just rinse with warm water and let air dry, restoring the gel pad to like new condition. No matter if your phone is protected by a skin or a case, the HD Universal Easy One Touch 2 Car Mount grips securely onto your device so you can drive with confidence. Mount Smart. Drive Smarter!

Name: iPhone 6/6S - Tempered Glass Screen Protector

The NANO SLIM for the iPhone 6 is made to cover and protect the LCD from damage and scratches with specially processed transparent glass that has been reinforced for scratch resistance. The 0.23mm thickness makes NANO SLIM compatible with all types of cases while still maintaining a surface hardness of 8~9H.

Key Features
• Covers and protects the LCD from damage and scratches
• Transparent glass that has been reinforced for scratch resistance
• Thickness : 0.23mm 
• Hardness : 8~9H

Brand + Name: OTTERBOX  Galaxy S4 - OtterBox Commuter Case
Description:
Compatibility:
◾Samsung Galaxy S4

•Sleek, protective case guards against scratches and drops
•Inner slip cover snugly wraps around the Galaxy S4
•Polycarbonate shell deflects impact shock from bumps and drops
•Self-adhesive screen protector guards against scratches to the touch screen

Features:
◾Full functionality of the device through the Commuter Series case 
◾Port covers protect the openings of the device from entry of dust and debris
◾Two layers of protection include an inner slip cover and a polycarbonate shell


Material:
◾Inner slip cover cushions the device against impact from drops and bumps
◾Polycarbonate outer layer provides solid protection that easily slips in and out of pockets
◾Self-adhering screen protector guards against scratches and smudges to the touch screen


Environmental Protection:
The Commuter Series for the Galaxy S4 provides added protection against bump and shock but is NOT protective against water.

Name: iPhone 6 Plus - Bumper 8 Case
Description:
The “Bumper 8” offers a sleek and slim design much like its predecessors to provide your phone with all round protection without compromising personality. The lightweight hard case is built using special UV pearl coating and matte SF coating cover provides scratch and shock protection for your iPhone. With a range of colours available, this phone is perfect for all styles!

  • 0.9mm thickness keeps the phone lightweight and comfortable to use
  • Slim and exact form-fitting for easy install/removal
  • Special UV pearl coating(white) and matte SF coating(black) cover provides scratch and shock protection for your phone, adding strength to the case 
  • Chrome-plated buttons(power and volumn) provide full acess to all features

Name: iPhone 6 - Persian Neo Case
Description:
The “Persian Neo” case has a tough yet lightweight plastic cover that makes a bold fashion statement while providing excellent protection for everyday knocks and drops. This stylish case is crafted with crystal rhinestones that are embedded into the back of the case with metallic polycarbonate edges to add a chic, sophisticated look for your phone. With precision design and fitting, the case will perfectly fit your phone for ergonomic ease. 

  • Beautiful design case with crystal rhinestone back and soft leather
  • Offers good protection for everyday use
  • Perfect fit allows easy install/remove and access to all ports and buttons

Name: iPhone 5 / 5S - Rich Diary Case
Description:
Rich Diary features a tough plastic TPU technology that protections your device from shock and everyday wear and tear. Just like a wallet, this case for your iPhone 5 or iPhone 5S offers card slot pocket that conveniently stores your important cards case. With precise cut-outs and iron made button, you will be able to talk with the cover closed without compromising your talk time.

- Tough TPU and hard-plastic construction for protection
- Talk with the cover closed
- Double inside card slot pocket & vertical cash sleeve gives you storage function to carry your ID or credit card conveniently
- Precise cut-outs and manufacturing to gives you full access to all control buttons, ports and camera

Name: iPhone 6 Plus - Rich Diary Case
Description:
The "Rich Diary" case features a tough plastic TPU technology that protections your device from shock and everyday wear and tear. Just like a wallet, this case for your iPhone 6 offers card slot pocket that conveniently stores your important cards case. With precise cut-outs and iron made button, you will be able to talk with the cover closed without compromising your talk time.

  • Tough TPU and hard-plastic construction for protection
  • Talk with the cover closed
  • Double inside card slot pocket & vertical cash sleeve gives you storage function to carry your ID or credit card conveniently
  • Precise cut-outs and manufacturing to gives you full access to all control buttons, ports and camera

Name: iPhone 6 Plus - Lifeproof Nuud Case
Brand + Name: LIFEPROOF  iPhone 6 Plus - Lifeproof Nuud Case
Description:
Lifeproof's "Nuud" is the lightest and thinnest case on offer from the premium brand. The slim hard case is purpose built to protect your phone from all the extremes - water, dirt, snow and shock. Perfect for any environment, the sleek, minimalistic case comes in black or white to offer subtle elegance for any user.

  • Screenless design lets you touch the actual Retina display
  • Thin, light and tough all-protective case
  • nüüd waterproof iPhone 6 Plus case works with Touch ID
  • Slim, sleek profile follows iPhone’s precision lines
  • Complete access to all buttons, ports and controls
  • Dynamic speaker ports deliver maximum sound output and clarity
  • Optimal protection, durability and style
  • Waterproof, dirt proof, snow proof and shockproof
  • Anti-reflective optical glass lens for distortion-free photography
  • Remains waterproof even when using headphones

Name: iPhone 5 / 5S - Bumper 8 Case
Description:
The "Bumper 8" case uses minimalism and subtlety to create a stylishly protective case. The signature "Bumper" features on the outer edges of the case, offering good protection against knocks, drops and scratches while remaining slim and lightweight. With a wide range of feature colours, this case is perfect for those looking for a case that offers great protection without compromising in style.

  • Slim 0.9mm thickness and smooth finish for comfortable grip 
  • Precision cut for easy install/remove

Name: iPhone 4 / 4S - Soft Case

• All iPHONE 4 / 4S buttons are easily accessible while resting in the case

Name: iPhone 6 - Lifeproof Nuud Case
Description:
Lifeproof's "Nuud" is the lightest and thinnest case on offer from the premium brand. The slim hard case is purpose built to protect your phone from all the extremes - water, dirt, snow and shock. Perfect for any environment, the sleek, minimalistic case comes in black or white to offer subtle elegance for any user.

  • Screenless design lets you touch the actual Retina display
  • Thin, light and tough all-protective case
  • nüüd waterproof iPhone 6 case works with Touch ID
  • Slim, sleek profile follows iPhone’s precision lines
  • Complete access to all buttons, ports and controls
  • Dynamic speaker ports deliver maximum sound output and clarity
  • Optimal protection, durability and style
  • Waterproof, dirt proof, snow proof and shockproof
  • Anti-reflective optical glass lens for distortion-free photography
  • Remains waterproof even when using headphones

Name: iPhone 6/ 6S Otterbox Defender Case
Description:
Defender Series iPhone 6s case completely covers your phone

Features:

  • Triple-layer, ultra rugged iPhone 6/ 6S cases made to survive the bumps, drops and scrapes you encounter on your adventures
  • Built-in screen protector shelters every inch of the 4.7” display, defending against scratches, scrapes and scuffs
  • Protective membrane cradles the Touch ID to block dust and debris and enhance device functionality
  • Belt-clip holster keeps your device handy and provides a mini-stand for hands-free use
  • Inner memory foam cushions the device while the outer slipcover absorbs impact

Rugged coverage

Defender Series is built tough to keep your device safe from drops, knocks and tumbles

Multitalented holster

Clips to most belts and straps and doubles as a kickstand

Completely covered

The all-over fit provides peak protection for your iPhone 6s

Name: iPhone 6 / 6S - Verus Mighty Card Defense Case
Brand + Name: iPhone 6 / 6S - Verus Mighty Card Defense Case
Description:
The Verus "Mighty Card Defense" allows you to ditch the wallet with the easy-access card slot on the back of the case. It comes in a range of versatile colours to complement a range of user styles. The "Mighty Card Defense" is a durable case designed to provide all-round protection through its impact-resistant TPU inner and polycarbonate outer as well as a raised front edge to stop screen scratches.

  • Variety of vibrant colours to suit all styles
  • Durable construction for everyday protection
  • Easy access card slot

Name: Samsung Galaxy S6 - Verus Mighty Card Defense Case
Brand + Name: Samsung Galaxy S6 - Verus Mighty Card Defense Case
Description:
The Verus "Mighty Card Defense" allows you to ditch the wallet with the easy-access card slot on the back of the case. It comes in a range of versatile colours to complement a range of user styles. The "Mighty Card Defense" is a durable case designed to provide all-round protection through its impact-resistant TPU inner and polycarbonate outer as well as a raised front edge to stop screen scratches.

  • Variety of vibrant colours to suit all styles
  • Durable construction for everyday protection
  • Easy access card slot

Name: Samsung Galaxy S6 - Verus Damda Slide Case

Description:

The hard case has a raised front edge providing scratch protection for the screen and a TPU body providing impact protection for your device.

  • Raised front edge for screen protection
  • Study impact resistant design
